{"image_id": "ZBRA_2018_page_71", "image_size": [1257, 1632], "ocr": [{"text": "68", "bbox": [618.0, 1579.7, 644.2, 1602.9]}, {"text": "The Company’s restricted stock grants consist of time-vested restricted stock awards (“RSAs”) and performance vested", "bbox": [93.8, 66.2, 1095.9, 89.3]}, {"text": "restricted stock awards (“PSAs”). The RSAs and PSAs hold voting rights and therefore are considered participating securities.", "bbox": [93.8, 94.9, 1152.7, 118.0]}, {"text": "The outstanding RSAs and PSAs are included as part of the Company’s Class A Common Stock outstanding. The RSAs and", "bbox": [93.8, 123.7, 1135.1, 146.8]}, {"text": "PSAs vest at each vesting date subject to restrictions such as continuous employment except in certain cases as set forth in each", "bbox": [93.8, 152.4, 1162.7, 175.6]}, {"text": "stock agreement. The Company’s RSAs and PSAs are expensed over the vesting period of the related award, which is typically", "bbox": [93.8, 181.2, 1159.8, 204.3]}, {"text": "3 years. Some awards, including those granted annually to non-employee directors as an equity retainer fee, were vested upon", "bbox": [93.8, 210.0, 1148.5, 233.1]}, {"text": "grant. PSA targets are set based on certain Company-wide financial metrics. Compensation cost is calculated as the market date", "bbox": [93.8, 238.7, 1162.8, 261.8]}, {"text": "fair value of the Company’s Class A Common Stock on grant date multiplied by the number of shares granted.", "bbox": [93.8, 267.5, 1020.1, 290.6]}, {"text": "The Company also issues stock awards to non-employee directors. Each director receives an equity grant of shares every year", "bbox": [93.8, 325.0, 1147.5, 348.1]}, {"text": "during the month of May. The number of shares granted to each director is determined by dividing the value of the annual grant", "bbox": [93.8, 353.8, 1163.1, 376.9]}, {"text": "by the price of a share of common stock. In fiscal 2018, there were 7,980 shares granted to non-employee directors compared to", "bbox": [93.8, 382.5, 1166.5, 405.6]}, {"text": "12,488 shares and 25,088 shares in fiscal 2017 and 2016, respectively. New directors in any fiscal year earned a prorated", "bbox": [93.8, 411.3, 1105.5, 434.4]}, {"text": "amount. The shares vest immediately upon the grant date.", "bbox": [93.8, 440.0, 580.2, 463.1]}, {"text": "A summary of information relative to the Company’s RSAs is as follows:", "bbox": [93.8, 497.5, 712.1, 520.7]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [515.9, 540.6, 562.8, 563.7]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [766.0, 540.6, 812.9, 563.7]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [1017.2, 540.6, 1064.0, 563.7]}, {"text": "Restricted Stock Awards", "bbox": [103.1, 639.9, 326.7, 663.0]}, {"text": "Shares", "bbox": [439.1, 639.9, 504.1, 663.0]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [548.4, 571.7, 639.9, 594.8]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [557.8, 595.7, 635.6, 618.8]}, {"text": "Grant Date", "bbox": [543.4, 619.7, 650.1, 642.8]}, {"text": "Fair Value", "bbox": [547.6, 643.6, 645.6, 666.7]}, {"text": "Shares", "bbox": [690.2, 639.9, 755.2, 663.0]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [799.4, 571.7, 890.9, 594.8]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [808.9, 595.7, 886.8, 618.8]}, {"text": "Grant Date", "bbox": [794.4, 619.7, 901.1, 642.8]}, {"text": "Fair Value", "bbox": [798.8, 643.6, 896.8, 666.7]}, {"text": "Shares", "bbox": [940.4, 639.9, 1005.4, 663.0]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [1050.7, 571.7, 1142.2, 594.8]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [1060.1, 595.7, 1137.9, 618.8]}, {"text": "Grant Date", "bbox": [1045.7, 619.7, 1152.4, 642.8]}, {"text": "Fair Value", "bbox": [1050.0, 643.6, 1148.0, 666.7]}, {"text": "Outstanding at beginning of year", "bbox": [128.2, 669.8, 412.7, 697.2]}, {"text": "628,642  $", "bbox": [446.4, 669.8, 546.2, 697.2]}, {"text": "77.70", "bbox": [602.7, 669.8, 662.9, 697.2]}, {"text": "622,814  $", "bbox": [698.5, 669.8, 798.3, 697.2]}, {"text": "70.19", "bbox": [852.9, 669.8, 913.0, 697.2]}, {"text": "566,447  $", "bbox": [948.7, 669.8, 1048.5, 697.2]}, {"text": "77.68", "bbo