ents granted, and the fair value is remeasured at the end of each reporting period", "bbox": [93.8, 1378.0, 1120.1, 1401.1]}, {"text": "based on the Company’s stock price. Cash settlement is based on the fair value of share equivalents at the time of vesting,", "bbox": [93.8, 1406.8, 1115.0, 1429.9]}, {"text": "which was $2 million, $2 million and $1 million in 2018, 2017 and 2016, respectively. Share-equivalents issued under these", "bbox": [93.8, 1435.5, 1132.8, 1458.6]}, {"text": "programs totaled 20,393, 45,781 and 95,210 in fiscal 2018, 2017 and 2016, respectively.", "bbox": [93.8, 1464.3, 835.8, 1487.4]}, {"text": "Non-qualified Stock Options", "bbox": [93.8, 1521.8, 336.3, 1544.9]}]}